{"tha-ap51:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap51:0.2":"Upalivagga ","tha-ap51:0.3":"Subhaddattheraapadana ","tha-ap51:1.1":"“Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap51:1.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap51:1.3":"Janatam uddharitvana, ","tha-ap51:1.4":"nibbayati mahayaso. ","tha-ap51:2.1":"Nibbayante ca sambuddhe, ","tha-ap51:2.2":"dasasahassi kampatha; ","tha-ap51:2.3":"Janakayo maha asi, ","tha-ap51:2.4":"deva sannipatum tada. ","tha-ap51:3.1":"Candanam purayitvana, ","tha-ap51:3.2":"tagaramallikahi ca; ","tha-ap51:3.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap51:3.4":"aropayim naruttamam. ","tha-ap51:4.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap51:4.2":"sattha loke anuttaro; ","tha-ap51:4.3":"Nipannakova sambuddho, ","tha-ap51:4.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap51:5.1":"‘Yo me pacchimake kale, ","tha-ap51:5.2":"gandhamalena chadayi; ","tha-ap51:5.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap51:5.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap51:6.1":"Ito cuto ayam poso, ","tha-ap51:6.2":"tusitakayam gamissati; ","tha-ap51:6.3":"Tattha rajjam karitvana, ","tha-ap51:6.4":"nimmanam so gamissati. ","tha-ap51:7.1":"Eteneva upayena, ","tha-ap51:7.2":"datva malam varuttamam; ","tha-ap51:7.3":"Sakakammabhiraddho so, ","tha-ap51:7.4":"sampattim anubhossati. ","tha-ap51:8.1":"Punapi tusite kaye, ","tha-ap51:8.2":"nibbattissatiyam naro; ","tha-ap51:8.3":"Tamha kaya cavitvana, ","tha-ap51:8.4":"manussattam gamissati. ","tha-ap51:9.1":"Sakyaputto mahanago, ","tha-ap51:9.2":"aggo loke sadevake; ","tha-ap51:9.3":"Bodhayitva bahu satte, ","tha-ap51:9.4":"nibbayissati cakkhuma. ","tha-ap51:10.1":"Tada sopagato santo, ","tha-ap51:10.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap51:10.3":"Upasankamma sambuddham, ","tha-ap51:10.4":"panham pucchissati tada. ","tha-ap51:11.1":"Hasayitvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap51:11.2":"sabbannu lokanayako; ","tha-ap51:11.3":"Punnakammam parinnaya, ","tha-ap51:11.4":"saccani vivarissati. ","tha-ap51:12.1":"Araddho ca ayam panho, ","tha-ap51:12.2":"tuttho ekaggamanaso; ","tha-ap51:12.3":"Sattharam abhivadetva, ","tha-ap51:12.4":"pabbajjam yacayissati. ","tha-ap51:13.1":"Pasannamanasam disva, ","tha-ap51:13.2":"sakakammena tositam; ","tha-ap51:13.3":"Pabbajessati so buddho, ","tha-ap51:13.4":"aggamaggassa kovido. ","tha-ap51:14.1":"Vayamitvanayam poso, ","tha-ap51:14.2":"sammasambuddhasasane; ","tha-ap51:14.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap51:14.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap51:15.1":"Pancamabhanavaram. ","tha-ap51:16.1":"Pubbakammena samyutto, ","tha-ap51:16.2":"ekaggo susamahito; ","tha-ap51:16.3":"Buddhassa oraso putto, ","tha-ap51:16.4":"dhammajomhi sunimmito. ","tha-ap51:17.1":"Dhammarajam upagamma, ","tha-ap51:17.2":"apucchim panhamuttamam; ","tha-ap51:17.3":"Kathayanto ca me panham, ","tha-ap51:17.4":"dhammasotam upanayi. ","tha-ap51:18.1":"Tassaham dhammamannaya, ","tha-ap51:18.2":"vihasim sasane rato; ","tha-ap51:18.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap51:18.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap51:19.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap51:19.2":"jalajuttamanayako; ","tha-ap51:19.3":"Nibbayi anupadano, ","tha-ap51:19.4":"dipova telasankhaya. ","tha-ap51:20.1":"Sattayojanikam asi, ","tha-ap51:20.2":"thupanca ratanamayam; ","tha-ap51:20.3":"Dhajam tattha apujesim, ","tha-ap51:20.4":"sabbabhaddam manoramam. ","tha-ap51:21.1":"Kassapassa ca buddhassa, ","tha-ap51:21.2":"tisso namaggasavako; ","tha-ap51:21.3":"Putto me oraso asi, ","tha-ap51:21.4":"dayado jinasasane. ","tha-ap51:22.1":"Tassa hinena manasa, ","tha-ap51:22.2":"vacam bhasim abhaddakam; ","tha-ap51:22.3":"Tena kammavipakena, ","tha-ap51:22.4":"paccha me asi bhaddakam. ","tha-ap51:23.1":"Upavattane salavane, ","tha-ap51:23.2":"pacchime sayane muni; ","tha-ap51:23.3":"Pabbajesi mahaviro, ","tha-ap51:23.4":"hito karuniko jino. ","tha-ap51:24.1":"Ajjeva dani pabbajja, ","tha-ap51:24.2":"ajjeva upasampada; ","tha-ap51:24.3":"Ajjeva parinibbanam, ","tha-ap51:24.4":"sammukha dvipaduttame. ","tha-ap51:25.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap51:25.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap51:25.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap51:26.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma subhaddo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap51:27.1":"Subhaddattherassapadanam navamam. "}